### Equipment Scheduling Validation API Examples

### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@companyCode = COMP001

### 1. Validar Agendamiento - POST (Equipo Disponible)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/EquipmentScheduling/validate?companyCode={{companyCode}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idEquipment": 2,
  "dateIni": "2025-08-23T00:00:00",
  "dateEnd": "2025-08-25T23:59:59"
}

